Class Centroid

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.Centroid

  • public class Centroid
extends java.lang.Object
    This class encapsulates the data structure and functionality behind a centriod of a cluster. Essentially, this object represents a point in 2D Euclidean space.
    Author:
    Nathan Minor
